data.description: This stunning home boasts an open concept layout, featuring a beautifully appointed kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The spacious primary bedroom and en suite are located on the main floor, with additional bedrooms, a game room, and loft upstairs. Situated in a prime location near the medical center, midtown, and downtown, this property offers easy access to the best dining, shopping, and entertainment in the area. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home! Schedule your showing appointment today!
